I obtained the updated flame1.cpp example from cvs, and I tried to 
run it.  I got the following error messages for these lines.  


    vector<Domain1D*> domains;
    domains.push_back(inlet);
    domains.push_back(flow);
    domains.push_back(surf);


(110) : error C2664: 'push_back' : cannot convert parameter 1 
from 'class Cantera::Inlet1D' to 'class Cantera::Domain1D *const & '

to 'class Cantera::Domain1D *const '

perform this conversion, or the operator cannot be called
